    <string name="tips_title">Quick tips</string>
    <string name="tips_body">&#8226; Face forward; sit in the front seat if you can.\n&#8226; Keep your eyes on the horizon, not on books or screens.\n&#8226; Crack a window — fresh, cool air helps.\n&#8226; Try ginger (chew, tea, or candy).\n&#8226; Stay hydrated; avoid heavy meals before travel.\n&#8226; If you feel queasy: breathe slowly and press P6.</string>

